        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Currently it looks like we cannot set help text for non-option arguments.\n\nFor example let's say my script allow one option  (--opt1|o) and one mandatory argument ('filename') so that usage is:\nUsage: myscript.php [ options ] _filename_\n--opt1|o    opt1 gets activated\n\n'filename' is not an option but an argument, without it the script is stopped.\nIt would be great to be able to add argument names that would be displayed when calling ->getUsageMessage();\n\nRegards,\nRemy Damour"
        },
